  # Post Create Item

  Creates a new item in the database.

  **Request:**
  ```json
  {
    "name": "string (required)",
    "description": "string (optional)",
    "price": "number (required)",
    "tax": "number (optional)"
  }
  ```

  **Success (201):**
  ```json
  {
    "message": "Item created successfully.",
    "data": {
      "id": 1,
      "name": "Sample Item",
      "description": "This is a sample item for testing",
      "price": 29.99
    }
  }
  ```
